{"tid":2180067,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台電子書商棄用支付寶   為保障平台毋須自行審查、下架政治敏感書籍","createTime":"2020-08-29T14:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T11:59:53.000Z","uid":51620,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10dba2983436edd7a5d5756f38133afd4384a445","tid":2180067,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"近日香港連串社會事件令國際關注，中國對政治議題相關討論、輿論大幅收緊。香港近日有華潤旗下便利店 VanGO 停售《蘋果日報》，而台灣亦有電子書服務商因為不希望平台受到政治審查，下架政治敏感書籍，於最近停止了平台的「支付寶」電子支付服務，香港、澳門、海外華語用戶需要改以 PayPal、信用卡等其他方式付款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/29/readmoo/life-tech/epayment/?fbclid=IwAR2lfaK0bLN1v-Lpfmr86oI9u2acX0Pc_9VInl0BopsiuZzCj_TKBYH553E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2Freadmoo%2Flife-tech%2Fepayment%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2lfaK0bLN1v-Lpfmr86oI9u2acX0Pc_9VInl0BopsiuZzCj_TKBYH553E&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLEWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=c7893637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/29/readmoo/life-tech/epayment/?fbclid=IwAR2lfaK0bLN1v-Lpfmr86oI9u2acX0Pc_9VInl0BopsiuZzCj_TKBYH553E</a>"},{"pid":"1b5aedfa417079adda0b7931880dbd90d80085b3","tid":2180067,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfc139b1ae8a921df3a134b18461c48e8c666ce","tid":2180067,"uid":306852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:44:54.000Z","msg":"Readmoo成日有折"},{"pid":"5ea187d9d3fa7907dd5f23ba47bf0e4ee89cfbf8","tid":2180067,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\